SECOND REGULAR SESSION
SENATE BILL NO. 1544
103RD GENERA L ASSEMBLY
INTRODUCED BY SENATOR NURRENBERN.
6571S.01I KRISTINA MARTIN, Secretary
AN ACT
To amend chapter 227, RSMo, by adding thereto one new section relating to the designation of
infrastructure.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
1 Section A. Chapter 227, RSMo, is amended by adding thereto
2 one new section, to be known as section 227.906, to read as
3 follows:
1 227.906. The portion of the State Highway 9 from
2 Horizons Parkway continuing north to Park College Entrance
3 Drive in Platte County shall be designated as "Firefighter
4 Paramedic Graham J Hoffman Memorial Highway". The
5 department of transportation shall erect and maintain
6 appropriate signs designating such highway, with the costs
7 to be paid by the department of transportation.
